page.title: 09Neal Ackroyd - Aged 8.
page.content: I'm{Neal Ackroyd.}I am 8 years old.I have brown eyes and hair.My birthday is August 6th.I live at Glenlee Road.My house is a semi-detached.My house is on an estate in the Bradford 7 area.I live with my mum,dad and brother.My mum's name is Corren.My dad's name is Martin and my brother's name is Gareth.My mum is aged 34.My dad is aged 34.My brother is 6.I like travelling on trains and buses.I like birthdays especially my own.Also,I like holidays and Christmas.At the moment it is my brother's birthday. Soon I will be going to Lidget Green Middle School.Next year my mum is going to get a new car.At the moment I am in Mr.Crosbie's class. My favourite {hobbies}are football and the computer.
